### --- Environments (Mamba/Conda/uv) ---
# We ignore the actual environment folders because they are huge.
# We recreate them using the lockfiles instead.
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
envs/
.conda/
conda-bld/

### --- IMPORTANT: uv/Dependency Files ---
# DO NOT ignore uv.lock or pyproject.toml. 
# They must be committed to GitHub.
# We only ignore the local tool settings if any:
.uv/

